OL,3,CGirl, 14, denies attempting to murder
OL,4,Cthree people at Ammanford school
OL,6,FA 14-year-old girl has denied the
OL,7,Fattempted murder of three people at a
OL,8,Fschool in Carmarthenshire.
OL,10,FYsgol Dyffryn Aman in Ammanford was
OL,11,Fput into lockdown on 24 April after
OL,12,Ftwo teachers and a pupil were
OL,13,Fallegedly stabbed.
OL,15,FThe teenage defendant, who cannot be
OL,16,Fnamed for legal reasons, appeared at
OL,17,FSwansea Crown Court on Monday, 12
OL,18,FAugust, for a plea and trial
OL,19,Fpreparation hearing.
