OL,3,CGirl, 14, denies attempting to murder
OL,4,Cthree people at Ammanford school
OL,6,FShe faces seven charges: three of
OL,7,Fattempted murder; three of wounding
OL,8,Fwith intent; and one of possession of
OL,9,Fa bladed article on a school premises
OL,10,Fin Ammanford, Carmarthenshire.
OL,12,FThe girl, who wore a white shirt,
OL,13,Fappeared in the dock at Swansea Crown
OL,14,FCourt on Monday, where she spoke to
OL,15,Fconfirm her name and enter her pleas.
OL,17,FShe denied the three counts of
OL,18,Fattempted murder but pleaded guilty to
OL,19,Fthe lesser charges of wounding with
OL,20,Fintent to cause grievous bodily harm,
OL,21,Fand possession of a bladed article.
