OL,3,CGirl, 14, denies attempting to murder
OL,4,Cthree people at Ammanford school
OL,6,FJudge Paul Thomas KC said the girl
OL,7,Fwould stand trial for the three counts
OL,8,Fof attempted murder next month.
OL,10,FAs the judge spoke the teenager looked
OL,11,Fat the ground.
OL,13,FThe trial was scheduled for September
OL,14,F30, with a pretrial review on
OL,15,FSeptember 17.
OL,17,FHelen Randall appeared on behalf of
OL,18,Fthe prosecution and Caroline Rees KC
OL,19,Fappeared on behalf of the defence.
