OL,6,FPupils at Ysgol Dyffryn Aman, also
OL,7,Fknown as Amman Valley School, went
OL,8,Finto lockdown on 24 April after the
OL,9,Falleged incident at the end of morning
OL,10,Fbreak.
OL,12,FTwo teachers, Fiona Elias and Liz
OL,13,FHopkin, and a pupil, were hurt in the
OL,14,Fincident but have since been released
OL,15,Ffrom hospital.
